# openlineage_job

Records an OpenLineage job and its full lineage metadata as a JSON file.
One file is written per job at `{output_dir}/{namespace}__{name}.json`.
The file contains the raw OpenLineage RunEvent alongside metadata for auditing.

Because this provider uses `FullJobCapability()`, **all** OpenLineage facets
are available and fully functional — schema, documentation, source code,
SQL, tags, column lineage, and more. Use the full example below as a
reference for the complete facet vocabulary.

